      <prov id="DLM3231200" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">33</label>
        <heading>Procedure for dealing with blood specimens</heading>
        <prov.body>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 74 is amended by repealing subsections (1) and (2) and substituting the following subsection:</text>
              <amend quote="1">
                <subprov skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">1</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>A blood specimen taken under section 72 or 73 must be dealt with in accordance with the relevant blood specimen collection procedure.</text>
                  </para>
                </subprov>
              </amend>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 74(3) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">both parts of the blood specimen to an approved analyst for the analysis of 1 of those parts and the custody of the other</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">the blood specimen to an approved laboratory for its analysis and custody in accordance with the relevant blood specimen collecting procedure</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 74(4)(a) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">both parts of the blood specimen to an approved analyst for the analysis of 1 of those parts and the custody of the other</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">the blood specimen to an approved laboratory for its analysis and custody in accordance with the relevant blood specimen collecting procedure</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">4</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 74(4)(b) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">give</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">if, at the time the blood specimen is taken, there is more than 1 approved laboratory, give</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">5</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 74(4)(b) is amended by repealing subparagraph (i) and substituting the following subparagraph:</text>
              <amend increment="2" quote="1">
                <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">i</label>
